    <data key="d0">Capgemini: Refactoring a Data Warehouse to Amazon Redshift</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5f3z1Z_9BJA</data>
    <data key="d2">HIPAA-compliant data platform migrating legacy Netezza to Redshift. Processes 100GB/day with automated S3 lifecycle transitions to Glacier.</data>
